io.fluo.api.data

Class RowColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.fluo.api.data.RowColumn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<RowColumn>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Notification, RowColumnValue

    public class RowColumn
extends Object
implements Comparable<RowColumn>, Serializable
    Represents all or subset of a Fluo row and Column. RowColumn is similar to an Accumulo Key. RowColumn is immutable after it is created.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
